name: statannot
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "statannot" %}
{% set version = "0.2.3" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 4600c2fa1f682d493a4ad0c1c4501b32a3d8d3a55877ec97bcf4e44fbd160cb9

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - python >=3.5
    - numpy
    - seaborn >=0.9.0
    - matplotlib-base
    - pandas
    - scipy >=1.1.0

test:
  imports:
    - statannot

about:
  home: "https://github.com/webermarcolivier/statannot"
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: "add statistical annotations on an existing boxplot/barplot generated by seaborn."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - Matt-BF
